# HANZO Platform Rules

## What HANZO Is

Controlled B2B trade platform: verified Chinese factories + Tanzanian/East African buyers. All communication and transactions go through HANZO.

## Factory Visibility (Never Violate)

Buyers must NOT see factory direct contact. Use `FactoryPrivacy::forBuyer($factory)` in controllers before passing to buyer views. Never expose `phone`, `email`, `wechat`, `whatsapp`, `contact_*`.

## MOQ

Every product displays Minimum Order Quantity. Product model has `moq`; show in all buyer product cards and detail views.

## Freight & Clearing

- **Freight rates**: Admin CRUD at `/admin/freight-rates` – sea/air, per CBM, per KG, per container
- **Clearing**: `config/clearing_rates.php` + Estimate Defaults (`customs_min`, `customs_max`)
- Used in Quote Builder and EstimatorService for cost estimation

## User Roles

- **Buyer** – products, RFQs, orders, platform messaging
- **Factory** – products, RFQs, orders (approved only)
- **HANZO Admin** – full control, freight, clearing, verification
